<h3>How do I donate to Christian Aid Ministries?</h3>
<p>
	If you would like to make a donation to Christian Aid Ministries, you can donate online at www.christianaidministries.org/donate or mail your donation to Christian Aid Ministries, P.O. Box 360, Berlin, OH 44610. You might also want to request our Gifts & Projects catalog for projects you can do and gifts you can give. All donations are tax-deductible. When making an online donation, you will receive an email receipt you can print for your records. You will receive a receipt by mail if you send the donation to our office. 
<br />
If you haven’t already done so, we invite you to visit our website at www.christianaidministries.org for more in-depth information about the countries in which we work, the people we help, and the projects we do.
</p>

<h3>Can Christian Aid Ministries assist my needs?</h3>
<p>
	If you requested funds or other assistance from Christian Aid Ministries, we regret to inform you that most of the funds we receive are already designated by donors toward specific projects. The funds we receive from donors are used 100 percent as designated for CAM programs and projects. We are not a lending agency.
</p>

